	(2161,'http://www.cars.com/admin/news/edit --- from[post] ----- http://www.cars.com/admin/news/edit/11.html','{&post(term_id)=>[161]&post(title)=>[华平合伙人陈伟豪：共享单车到底是要烧出流量入口，还是烧出自我造血的公司？]&post(summary)=>[打还是合，最后还是资本说了算]&post(from)=>[创投人说]&post(author)=>[王海璐]&post(_tags)=>[共享单车,摩拜单车,小黄单车,哈罗单车,共享汽车,混动汽车]&post(tags)=>[165,168,167,166,164,170]&post(content)=>[<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\">在华平合伙人、中国消费组负责人陈伟豪看来，出行市场的未来充满变化，有大量价值可供挖掘。而华平迄今为止的投资布局，已经为占领出行市场的高地打下根基。</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\">如果两家公司无法合并，那么下一步，<span xss=removed>ofo可能不得不向战略股东投降，得到战略股东的输血，并成为大平台生态的一部分。这场单车大战的终局，将会变得更加耐人寻味。</span>但摩拜身后也站着一个大平台，腾讯是不太可能袖手旁观的。陈伟豪对此未做评论，但表示最快1个月内，局势就会变得更清晰。</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\">“哪怕最后阿里、腾讯、滴滴全部在这里面，大家到底希望烧出什么？是烧一个流量入口出来，还是烧一个真正能够自我造血的公司出来。<span xss=removed>很多人说这是一个神仙打架游戏，我们先把资本上的杂音去除，回头来看一下商业本质和产品。我相信一个好产品和一个好公司，势必会拿到更多资本，而且有可能变成一个独立的平台。</span>”陈伟豪说。</p>\r\n\r\n<p alt=\"华平合伙人陈伟豪：共享单车到底是要烧出流量入口，还是烧出自我造血的公司？\" class=\"load-html-img loaded\" data-img-size-val=\"1034,690\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" img=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" src=\"https://pic.36krcnd.com/avatar/201801/19031027/4id6tkkmat0cv7sk.jpg!1200\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\">除了共享单车，华平还重金押注汽车零售市场，投资优信、大搜车，并考虑在这条赛道继续布局。有二手车行业的人士向36氪透露，优信、瓜子、人人车，目前都在进行新一轮融资。陈伟豪认为，汽车零售电商的市场足够大，B2C, C2C，只要业务模式合理，每个细分领域是有可能生长出一、两家公司的。</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\">在赋能车商方面，陈伟豪认为，建立在SaaS系统之上、为车商管理库存和供应链的大搜车具有更大的优势。华平领投了大搜车D轮融资，去年11月，阿里领投大搜车3.35亿美金，华平又再次跟投。陈伟豪是大搜车的董事会成员，他告诉36氪，早在2012年，大搜车创始人姚军红离开神州创业时他就在关注，“等了他4年时间”，看着他把业务模式基本“趟出来”了，才决定投资。他认为姚军红做经销商的一段创业经历，以及大搜车服务车商的基础，将成为建立与车商之间的粘性的一个重要抓手。</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\">汽车分期降低了用户的准入门槛。但在陈伟豪看来，这个市场还不会那么轻易被打穿。<span xss=removed>汽车产业链条复杂，主机厂掌握着强势的话语权，4S店是僵硬但稳固的存量渠道，和主机厂之间有着多年合作的信任关系，以及盘根错节的利益关联。</span>在渠道的分发上，主机厂可能会优先照顾主渠道4S店的利益。把优质车源给到4S店。因此，陈伟豪认为，汽车零售电商们相互厮杀之前，和4S店之间还有一场渠道战要打。</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span class=\"load-html-img loaded\" xss=removed><img alt=\"华平合伙人陈伟豪：共享单车到底是要烧出流量入口，还是烧出自我造血的公司？\" data-img-size-val=\"809,539\" src=\"https://pic.36krcnd.com/avatar/201801/19030706/pm2szamusr5lpl2s.jpeg!1200\" xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"img-desc\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>以下是36氪专访华平合伙人陈伟豪的部分内容整理：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>共享单车的战局最近又有了一些新变化。两家如果不合并，继续打下去，最后的结果就是一家把另一家打死？</h3>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>摩拜最近布局打车、分时租赁，好像有一个四轮车的梦想？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>摩拜做分时租赁和投资人交流过吗？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>现在美团也做打车、分时租赁。跟美团合作，还是跟ofo合并，对摩拜更有好处？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>华平关注过分时租赁市场吗？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>但是你们没有投？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>这门生意最难的是什么？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" h3=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\">二手车电商做新车，拿车的能力很重要</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>陈伟豪：</span>我们要看，这个赛道够大，但是细分领域的逻辑是不是合理。为什么瓜子和人人车一直都没有投，因为最早的时候我们对C2C是有一个问号的。但是这是我们现在静态眼光来看，如果放长3-5年以后，是不是通过技术革新会做得更好，或者这个趋势会来得多快，我们现在需要做一个判断。</p>\r\n\r\n<p alt=\"华平合伙人陈伟豪：共享单车到底是要烧出流量入口，还是烧出自我造血的公司？\" class=\"load-html-img\" data-=\"\" data-img-size-val=\"5616,3353\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" img=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" src=\"https://pic.36krcnd.com/avatar/201801/19033337/4h80yll0kb7t8orr.jpg!1200\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>华平投资二手车的逻辑是什么？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>这个时间会持续多久？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>大搜车的弹个车去年很火，阿里也投了，你们为什么会投？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>他们和其他汽车零售电商有什么差别？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>优信也在做新车分期，借助金融可以完成商业闭环吗？听说优信要上市了。</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>为什么现在二手车都开始做新车了？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span xss=removed>36氪：</span>大家都在做新车，到底谁能做出来，最主要的因素是什么？</p>\r\n\r\n<p font-size:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" lantinghei=\"\" micro=\"\" microsoft=\"\" p=\"\" pingfang=\"\" span=\"\" xss=removed wenquanyi=\"\" zen=\"\"><span class=\"load-html-img loaded\" xss=removed><img alt=\"华平合伙人陈伟豪：共享单车到底是要烧出流量入口，还是烧出自我造血的公司？\" data-img-size-val=\"7360,4912\" src=\"https://pic.36krcnd.com/avatar/201801/19030833/joodkgtx8jum065m.jpeg!1200\" xss=removed></span></p>\r\n]&post(SEOKeywords)=>[汽车,交通出行,电商二手车,共享单车,零售,腾讯,优信]&post(SEODescription)=>[打还是合，最后还是资本说了算]&post(sort)=>[0]&post(views)=>[999]&post(thumb)=>[]&post(is_issue)=>[1]&post(id)=>[11]}','127.0.0.1','2018-01-24 18:29:21',9),
