x-width: 100%; margin: 30px auto; border-radius: 5px; width: 720px; height: auto;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','打还是合，最后还是资本说了算','0',999,'0','1','汽车,交通出行,电商二手车,共享单车,零售,腾讯,优信','打还是合，最后还是资本说了算','','2018-01-24 18:29:21','2018-01-24 11:29:31',0,9,'cn'),
	(12,161,'滴滴共享单车平台登陆北京深圳，用户可免押金骑小蓝单车','70272070 70272069 69-271768 68261169 69-19-1172 72290669 69251969 69-171671 71-72773 73-7-2669 69-20-968 68261270 70231769 71-120870 70-242369 69-171569 69-27-1970 70-222873 73-25-1573 7310-1569 6916-1772 72-13-369','36氪','GentlemanZ','165,166,167,168','&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;load-html-img loaded&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;滴滴共享单车平台登陆北京深圳，用户可免押金骑小蓝单车&quot; data-img-size-val=&quot;859,611&quot; src=&quot;https://pic.36krcnd.com/avatar/201801/17030506/a965mo8nv5fja24g.jpg!1200&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; opacity: 1; transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 30px auto; border-radius: 5px; width: 720px; height: auto;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;1月17日消息，36氪获悉，滴滴共享单车平台（滴滴出行APP内标签为&amp;ldquo;单车&amp;rdquo;）今日将在北京、深圳上线，平台目前包括小蓝单车和ofo小黄车，其中小蓝单车将免押金骑行。滴滴希望以此优化共享单车用户体验、促进社会信用体系建设。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;load-html-img loaded&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;滴滴共享单车平台登陆北京深圳，用户可免押金骑小蓝单车&quot; data-img-size-val=&quot;646,1288&quot; src=&quot;https://pic.36krcnd.com/avatar/201801/17030337/g4ochi5tukqzhvzs.jpg!1200&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; opacity: 1; transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 30px auto; border-radius: 5px; width: 646px; height: auto;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;img-desc&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: -10px auto 15px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); text-align: center; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px; font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;滴滴出行APP界面&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;滴滴方面透露，除了免押金骑行，滴滴还将联合城市监管部门及其他合作伙伴，共同优化共享单车使用流程和停放秩序，让共享出行事业实现可持续增长。未来，滴滴共享单车平台将登陆其他城市。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;近期滴滴陆续对小蓝单车各地业务进行了托管，用户将可以通过滴滴APP中的&amp;ldquo;单车&amp;rdquo;标签再次骑行小蓝单车。【注：需更新至滴滴出行APP5.1.28版】北京深圳是首批城市，经过滴滴维修后的小蓝单车，也将陆续重新回归城市。在滴滴平台进行芝麻信用认证后，用户可以免押金骑行小蓝单车。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;load-html-img&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;滴滴共享单车平台登陆北京深圳，用户可免押金骑小蓝单车&quot; data-=&quot;&quot; data-img-size-val=&quot;853,568&quot; src=&quot;https://pic.36krcnd.com/avatar/201801/17030624/6i68q4acb1zjej10.jpg!1200&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 30px auto; border-radius: 5px; width: 720px; height: 479.437px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;img-desc&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: -10px auto 15px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); text-align: center; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px; font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;维修后的小蓝单车重新回到城市&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;去年5月，交通部出台《关于鼓励和规范互联网租赁自行车发展的指导意见》，旨在鼓励和规范互联网租赁自行车发展，提升互联网租赁自行车服务水平，优化交通出行结构，构建绿色、低碳的出行体系。意见强调，要加强用户资金安全监管，鼓励互联网租赁自行车运营企业采用免押金方式提供租赁服务。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;滴滴出行高级副总裁付强表示，滴滴希望通过共享单车平台升级短途出行战略，为&amp;ldquo;最后三公里&amp;rdquo;用户提供更丰富的出行选择、更良好的出行体验，并以此不断完善滴滴的一站式出行平台建设。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 26px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lantinghei SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&amp;quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, &amp;quot;\\\\5B8B体&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;根据托管安排，小蓝单车的品牌、押金和欠款等各项事务仍归属于小蓝公司。滴滴将提供&amp;ldquo;小蓝单车APP用户押金、特权卡及充值余额可转换为等值滴滴单车券和出行券&amp;rdquo;的备选方案，用户可自主选择，或与小蓝公司继续沟通其他方案。滴滴同时公布了押金等的具体转换方案，充值余额可转换为等值单车券，押金和特权卡可转换为等值单车券或单车券与出行券（无门槛现金抵用券）的组合，用户转换之后即可使用相应抵用券。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','共享单车行业生变~','0',999,'0','1','交通出行,滴滴,共享单车','共享单车行业生变~','uploads/2018/01/24/images/201801241137402712.jpg','2018-01-24 11:37:52','2018-01-24 11:37:52',0,9,'cn');
